Bash Projects
=============

* Network scanner: netscan.sh
* IPv4 Networking: iptx.sh, ipv4.md
* S-nail setup: snail.sh
* SSH: sshban.sh
* OTP encryption: otpcrypt.sh, cryptinfo.md
* Metadata: delmeta.sh
* Apache2 setup: apache2.sh
* Sysops utilities: sysutil.sh
* Security auditing: scansec/, auditscan.sh
* Deployment: deploy.sh, deploy.conf
* Android: android_cleanup.sh, packages_to_remove.txt, package_urls.txt
* Content folding: linecutter.sh
* Web scraping: scrapexkcd.sh
* CLI Plotting: cliplot.sh
* Data toolkit: df/
* CF computations: finbot.sh
* Traffic generator: tg.sh, config.json
